data.description: Elegant 4 bedroom, 3.5 baths with a beautifully maintained yard.  Gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, with stainless steel appliances, ample granite countertops and custom cabinetry complete with plenty of storage space.  The adjacent dining area can double as a flex space offering a cozy atmosphere for enjoying meals or entertaining with family and friends.  The large family room is perfect for cozy movie nights or hosting entertaining events.  The oversized primary bedroom boasts an en-suite bathroom, complete with a luxurious soaking tub, separate oversized walk-in shower and double vanity.  Generous sized bedrooms and ample storage are an added bonus.  Upstairs flex space is complete with a full bath and balcony overlooking the beautiful green space it backs up too. Water purification and smart home features are an added bonus to an already complete home.  Located in a prime location close to local amenities and major highways, which makes commuting a breeze.
